text: Ærest on Hornesbeorg.
Of ðam beorge on leas ende on Corfget.
Of ðam gete on cruc middeweardne.
Ðonne of cruc on ðone smalan hricg.
Andlang hricges on hlyda pol.
Of ðam pole andlang streames on fyrsford.
Of ðam forda andlang readan hyrstes to hlypegete.
Fram hlypegete to ðam colpytte.
Fram colpette to ðam healfan treowe.
Ðanne forðrihtes on Browoldes heal, and ðanon on staford upp ongean stream.
Of ðam streame on stochylle.
Of stochylle on fogga crundel easteweardne.
Of ðam crundele forð be wyrtruman on Brumdun middeweardne.
Of Brumdune on murtes wyll.
Of murtes wylle ongean stream on Tollor æwylman.
Of ðam æwylman on Cotte dene.
Of Cotta dene on ruwan beorg.
Of ðam beorge on rigcumb middeweardne.
Of rigcumbe on gyrdlea middeweardne.
Of gyrdlea on ðone stanigan weg.
Of ðam wege on ðone wæter pytt.
Of ðam pytte on Coccelmæres dene.
Of ðære dene on earne dene.
Of earna dene eft on Hornesbeorg.
